#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:10
msgid "Merkuro Calendar"
msgstr "Calendari de Merkuro"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:11
msgid "Manage your tasks and events with speed and ease"
msgstr "Gestioneu les tasques i esdeveniments amb rapidesa i facilitat"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:18
msgid ""
"Merkuro Calendar is a calendar application that allows you to manage your "
"tasks and events. Kalendar supports both local calendars as well as a "
"multitude of online calendars: Nextcloud, Google® Calendar, Outlook®, "
"Caldav, and many more."
msgstr ""
"El Calendari de Merkuro és una aplicació de calendari que permet gestionar "
"les tasques i esdeveniments. Dona suport a dos calendaris locals, així com "
"una multitud de calendaris en línia: NextCloud, Google® Calendar, Outlook®, "
"Caldav i molts més."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:19
msgid ""
"Merkuro gives you many ways to interact with your events. The month view "
"provides an overview of the entire month; the week view presents a detailed "
"hour-by-hour overview of your week; and the schedule view lists all of your "
"upcoming events so that you can easily and quickly plan ahead."
msgstr ""
"Merkuro oferix moltes maneres d'interactuar amb els esdeveniments. La vista "
"mensual proporciona una visió general de tot el mes. La vista setmanal "
"presenta una visió general detallada de la vostra setmana. I la vista de "
"llista enumera tots els pròxims esdeveniments de manera que pugueu "
"planificar amb facilitat i rapidesa."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:20
msgid ""
"A tasks view is also available, making it possible for you to manage your "
"tasks and subtasks with Merkuro's powerful tree view and its customisable "
"filtering capabilities."
msgstr ""
"També hi ha disponible una vista de tasques, la qual permet gestionar les "
"tasques i subtasques amb la potent vista en arbre de Merkuro i les seues "
"capacitats personalitzables de filtratge."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.merkuro.calendar.metainfo.xml:21
msgid ""
"Merkuro was built with the idea to be usable on desktop, on mobile and "
"everything in between."
msgstr ""
"Merkuro s'ha construït amb la idea de ser utilitzable en l'escriptori, en el "
"mòbil i tot el que hi ha entre ells."

